{"word":"ἐπίδηλος","slug":"ἐπίδηλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπίδηλος</b></el> <el>(ἐπ-ίδηλος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εἶδον'><el>εἶδον</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>seen clearly, manifest</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>distinguished, remarkable</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>like, resembling</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}